common/

Reusable backend building blocks live here. Keep cross-cutting code in this
folder when it is shared by more than one module.

Current responsibilities:
- decorators: route metadata helpers
- filters: global exception response shaping
- guards: authentication and role guards
- interceptors: logging and response shaping
- middlewares: request-level Express middleware
- pipes: validation and parsing helpers
- utils: framework-neutral helper functions
